d Mary de Holland about 1170, in Hale, Lancashire, England, United Kingdom. They were the parents of at least 1 son. He died in 1177, in Halewood, Lancashire, England, United Kingdom, at the age of 26."},"et":{"1151–1177":"1151–1177","1153–1181":"1153–1181","1177–1235":"1177–1235","about 1170":"umbes 1170","1235":"1235","1177":"1177","1153":"1153","1151":"1151","1181":"1181","Hale, Lancashire, England, United Kingdom":"Hale, Lancashire, Inglismaa, United Kingdom","Hale, Lancashire, England":"Hale, Lancashire, England","Halewood, Lancashire, England":"Halewood, Lancashire, Inglismaa, United Kingdom"},"fi":{"1151–1177":"1151–1177","1153–1181":"1153–1181","1177–1235":"1177–1235","about 1170":"noin 1170","1235":"1235","1177":"1177","1153":"1153","1151":"1151","1181":"1181","Hale, Lancashire, England, United Kingdom":"Hale, Lancashire, Englanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta","Hale, Lancashire, England":"Hale, Lancashire, England","Halewood, Lancashire, England":"Halewood, Lancashire, Englanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta"},"fr":{"1151–1177":"1151–1177","1153–1181":"1153–1181","1177–1235":"1177–1235","about 1170":"environ 1170","1235":"1235","1177":"1177","1153":"1153","1151":"1151","1181":"1181","Hale, Lancashire, England, United Kingdom":"Hale, Lancashire, Angleterre, Royaume-Uni","Hale, Lancashire, England":"Hale, Lancashire, Angleterre","Halewood, Lancashire, England":"Halewood, Lancashire, Angleterre, Royaume-Uni","lifeSummary":"William de Columbers est né en 1151, à Halewood, Lancashire, Angleterre. Il a épousé Mary de Holland environ 1170, à Hale, Lancashire, Angleterre, Royaume-Uni. Ils ont eu au moins 1 fils. Il est décédé en 1177, à Halewood, Lancashire, Angleterre, Royaume-Uni, à l’âge de 26 ans."},"de":{"1151–1177":"1151–1177","1153–1181":"1153–1181","1177–1235":"1177–1235","about 1170":"um 1170","1235":"1235","1177":"1177","1153":"1153","1151":"1151","1181":"1181","Hale, Lancashire, England, United Kingdom":"Hale, Lancashire, England, United Kingdom","Hale, Lancashi